One of the best video documentaries ever on our beautiful Darjeeling. It is an amazing experience to experience Darjeeling in reality but this video captures those details and angles kudos to the drone shots, that one canâ€™t experience in person. The writing, concept, narration, shooting, angles, colouring, video editing and most importantly choice of apt background music, makes this videography and production simply top notch. Every second of this video left me mesmerised and in awe and at the end when the music faded away it left a very fulfilling feeling of nostalgia.
